    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050600/extras/34d1a45d4f1e558df1707976e382d474.poster.avif?t=1719563508\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050600/extras/34d1a45d4f1e558df1707976e382d474.webm?t=1719563508\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050600/extras/34d1a45d4f1e558df1707976e382d474.mp4?t=1719563508\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Do You Like Exorcism?</h2>Calling the name of the demon.<br>That is the essence of exorcism.<br>What is the identity of the demon possessing the child?<br>Using information about the demon's origin and rank from the list of demons recorded in the holy texts, combine logical reasoning with a bit of luck to choose the demon's name.<br>If you get it right, you win. If you get it wrong, you'll be cornered.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050600/extras/8145d1fbefd927ed000303ea9a70647b.poster.avif?t=1719563508\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050600/extras/8145d1fbefd927ed000303ea9a70647b.webm?t=1719563508\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050600/extras/8145d1fbefd927ed000303ea9a70647b.mp4?t=1719563508\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Exorcist Seeking Names V.S. Demon Seeking Sins</h2>Up to 10 demons can invade your house, approaching to learn about your greatest sins.<br>You must identify which demon is possessing the child while avoiding interference.<br>Each play session lasts about 30 minutes, but you can enjoy the strategic back-and-forth multiple times.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050600/extras/8d7022934a42d5f36c660549a28b8473.poster.avif?t=1719563508\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050600/extras/8d7022934a42d5f36c660549a28b8473.webm?t=1719563508\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050600/extras/8d7022934a42d5f36c660549a28b8473.mp4?t=1719563508\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Challenge Fate with Everything Given</h2>With over 20 different &quot;holy verses&quot; that can be randomly obtained, you can gain various pieces of information and advantages.<br>Using the gathered information, identify the demon in front of you.<br>Even if you throw all your saved holy verses into the fight, there aren't many moments where you can be 100% sure.<br>There will be times when you must challenge with a success rate of 50%, 30%, or even 10%.<br>Pray that you're right. This is a slightly complex game of chance and a battle spiced up with some &quot;divine intervention.&quot;<br>Do you like games of chance?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050600/extras/f1c5063e950dd42b5ec716d84b1b2aea.poster.avif?t=1719563508\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050600/extras/f1c5063e950dd42b5ec716d84b1b2aea.webm?t=1719563508\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050600/extras/f1c5063e950dd42b5ec716d84b1b2aea.mp4?t=1719563508\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Holy Verses Carved as the Last Weapon</h2>Each time you save a child, you can carve a holy verse into the cross.<br>This allows you to control which holy verses you can obtain to some extent, supporting your gameplay against luck.<br>If you save 5 children and exorcise what lies beyond the 6th door, you can leave the house of demons.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050600/extras/be17157d730a4d5c37cdc7d7b2a9dcfa.poster.avif?t=1719563508\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050600/extras/be17157d730a4d5c37cdc7d7b2a9dcfa.webm?t=1719563508\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050600/extras/be17157d730a4d5c37cdc7d7b2a9dcfa.mp4?t=1719563508\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【Streaming and Broadcasting Guidelines】</h2>We welcome game play videos from individuals and corporations, but please make sure to read and comply with the following guidelines:<br><br>・Include the game title &quot;Exorcist: Reviewer of Minds&quot; in the title of your videos or live streams.<br>・Provide a link to the store page in accessible places such as the description section.<br>・Monetization through features provided by video sites (advertising revenue, donations, etc.) is allowed.<br>・Do not include content that defames or slanders others, or that is contrary to public order and morals in your game commentary or broadcasts.<br>・727 NOT HOUND is not responsible for any damages or issues that arise from the commentary or broadcasting of the game.<br>・These guidelines may be changed without notice, and the revised guidelines will apply to videos created after the change.",
